        "timestamp": "2022-11-28 15:02:50.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review-2\n\nSome issues:\n- When adding a value to map, the checkbox only appears after entering the key\n- When addind a value to map which already contains values, and then selecting the TOSCA Function for the newly added value, the value from one of the already existing values is shown\n- The right hand border of the value field cannot be seen once the checkbox appears\n- The TOSCA function button can be selected when two map entries are selected\n- The delete button for the map entry disappears after entering a TOSCA function value\n- Adding value of complex type doesnt seem to work anymore, i.e. only a text field is displayed for value instead of showing all the properties of the complex type",
