          "username": "MichaelMorris"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2022-11-30 12:59:49.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nMaps of complex types still not displayed correctly\n\nAlso I have seen several issues with setting tosca values in a map contained within a complex type property\n- when adding a yaml TOSCA function value to a map property in a complex type, the key is being replaced by an id\n- this entry cannot then be deleted\n- when adding get_property TOSCA function to a map property in a complex type, the UI hangs with an error in the console\n\n\nFor the checkbox, I think it would be better if it was present and disabled (if needs be) until the key is entered rather than just appearing as the user starts entering a key\n\nThe checkbox also appears to move behind the key field as I decrease the zoom level in my browser",
        "patchset_number": 3
      },
